ğŸ’§ AI Water Intake Tracker

An end-to-end AI-powered water intake tracking application built to understand how frontend, backend, database, and AI work together in a real-world project.

This project is learning-focused, beginner-friendly, and intentionally designed with clear separation of responsibilities so anyone can understand the full system flow.

ğŸš€ What does this project do?

Lets users log water intake (in ml)

Stores intake data persistently using SQLite

Calculates daily total intake

Shows remaining water based on daily goal

Provides AI-generated motivational feedback

Displays intake history & line graph for easy understanding

